    quarter_of_the_year formula [note: 'business desc: his formula determines the quarter (Q1, Q2, Q3, or Q4) for the date in start_date and appends the respective year. The first part uses the month to calculate which quarter the date falls into; the second part adds the four-digit year. As a result, regardless of whether the date is in a past, current, or future year, you’ll see the quarter followed by the year, such as “Q3 2022” or “Q1 2025.” This is useful for quickly identifying the specific quarter and year of any given date., technical desc: Type: formula, field ID: fldhQ34ULcjrIJH99']
    active_campaign singleLineText [note: 'business desc: Indicates if a campaign is currently running. Stores a boolean value (true/false)., technical desc: Type: singleLineText, field ID: fldDerbCTYrU2RXYF']
    ai_context multilineText [note: 'business desc: Generates a JSON object containing key campaign details from specified fields., technical desc: Type: multilineText, field ID: fldPpwAv2LiLPSwzd']
    clients multipleRecordLinks [note: 'business desc: Connects advertisers with their client accounts. Provides access to client information., technical desc: Type: multipleRecordLinks, Reference to advertisers table, field ID: fldw0a19GPw6dAFar']
    first_ai_summary multilineText [note: 'business desc: A summary of the first AI analysis results., technical desc: Type: multilineText, field ID: fldVgJ0PMil84RjEo']
    first_ai_strategic_insights multilineText [note: 'business desc: First AI strategic insights; initial analysis & recommendations., technical desc: Type: multilineText, field ID: fld2ADUCGvaTXgSwd']
    jwt_anonymous multilineText [note: 'business desc: Stores a JSON Web Token for anonymous users., technical desc: Type: multilineText, field ID: fldVvcTbYWyeuqTTz']
    note: '### project_brief_test Table (airtable id: tblir5UlRHvWIueK5) - This table consolidates all necessary data for evaluating and processing campaign briefs submitted by clients. It includes contact information, campaign details, target demographics, media preferences, geography targeting, and workflow status. This structure ensures standardized data collection, review, and collaboration for streamlined campaign approval and execution workflows within the Grassroots CRM platform.'
}

